      "text": "Last year in the richest nation on Earth, nearly half of adults under 30 lived with a parent.\n\nIn America, owning a home shouldn't be a pipe dream.\n\nMaybe, just maybe, instead of spending trillions on tax breaks for the rich and more wars, we should invest in affordable housing.",
