      "text": "Dr. Hussam Abu Safiya ran one of Gaza's last hospitals. He refused to leave his patients even after Israel killed his own son in a drone strike.\n\nIsrael kidnapped him for it. 18 months in detention, tortured and beaten, for the crime of running a hospital.\n\nHe must be released.",
